Setup		soundwave


Zmin 		0.0
Zmax 		1.0

Amplitude	1.0e-4

RHOG		1.0
DENSGR		1.0
DENSGI		0.0
TGAS        1.0
TDUST       1.0

Gamma		1.4
CPDG		0.01
SOUNDWAVE_USE_PAR_TS	1
