REAL_EIGEN		-1.0988402477744863
IMAG_EIGEN		7.19531036614774244

DT		    0.01
Ninterm	 	1
Ntot		500

PeriodicZ	Yes
Nz		    64
CFL         0.3 
OutputDir  	outputs/sw_run
